Perhaps, the most popular way to measure NC/nanostructure QYs is to compare their integrated emission intensities to that of a known QY reference (usually an organic dye) under identical measurement conditions. The QY can then be estimated using7QY=QYrefIsIrefArefAsnsolventnref2,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
