				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathrm{QY}_{\mathrm{absolute}} = \frac{{\mathrm{QY}_{\mathrm{observed}}}}{{1 - r\left( {1 - \mathrm{QY}_{\mathrm{Observed}}} \right)}},$$\end{document}where r is the reabsorption probability, estimated from the ratio of integrated emission intensities of concentrated and dilute NC/nanostructure solutions82.

